title: SZ1 Presents: WestBam
description: A legend of rave and early techno music, one of the founding members and Members Of Mayday and a stringpusher behind the old Berlin's Love Parade. To we have to add much more?

title: WeAreRadar x Nurt: Fixmer
description: Radar Crew returns to our humble cellar with lots of excitement from ours an their sides. Also supported by a thriving and newer initiative of Nurt Festival. The headliner, who is a French artist that probably invented the whole 'techno body music' genre, in other words - a style of EBM fit for regular clubs and not just goth parties, is also a symbol here.

title: Szpitalne Jajca
description: On Easter saturday we meet and dance wouthout excessible fireworks. Our residents will provide all the stuff the need...

title: Neurodydaktyka pres. Goldie
description: The stringpushers behind our regular bass music party decided to throw a big shot this time. Returning back to the roots - as Goldie in considered as one of the inventors of jungle and drum'n'bass music - is also remarkable here.

title: SZ1 Presents: David Vunk
description: The beast and the ogre of Rotterdam standing behind Moustache Records label might look scary at first look but his music sometimes speaks otherwise. Come around, watch and listen and you definitely won't be dissapointed by anythig at this party ;)

title: TECHNO TECHYES pres. D.A.V.E. The Drummer
description: TECHNO TECHYES regulars return with their usual warranty of good fun supported by a hard techno legend from the UK. Come around and check what will be going on this time...

title: SZ1 Presents: Kerri Chandler
description: A house legend from New York supported by a an extremely active, local house DJ and promoter. We're sure that they will find a common tongue.

title: Majówkowe Pląsy
description: Our residents night is an ideal option for a chilling May holiday evening.

title: Szpitalniany Salon Ambientu pres. Celestial Trax
description: Cykl wydarzeń o nazwie „Salon Ambientu” rozpoczął się w Białymstoku i wywodzi się z działań festiwalu Up To Date oraz kolektywu Technosoul. Dotychczas odbyło się kilkadziesiąt edycji w wielu miastach Polski. Organizując Salony Ambientu, skupiamy się na promocji takich gatunków jak ambient, modern classical, IDM, a nawet noise. Kulminacyjnym momentem roku jest Centralny Salon Ambientu odbywający się w ramach festiwalu Up To Date rokrocznie we wrześniu.

title: Empire Of Marching Groove
description: W ramach tego cyklu prezentujemy zarówno marszowe jak i bardziej połamane odmiany elektroniki.

title: Another Residents' Night
description: What about just another residents' night?

title: Piorun #7
description: Is Tomasz aka Ultraviolent a daredevil to launch his own regular party at this time in world's history? We shall see...

title: SZ1 Presents: DanceFloorplan
description: The well-known priest of techno accompanied by an appriopate companionship. We should definitely say 'be there or be square' and this time it's not a cliche.
